1
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,160
Biar saya beritahu awak.

2
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:41,720
Pergi ke Beijing itu perkara kecil sahaja.

3
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,560
Cakap nak pergi, terus pergi.

4
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,640
Apa yang hebat sangat?

5
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,800
Awak pergi mana sahaja?

6
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,720
Masa itu kami pergi ke...

7
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:48,160
Masa saya kecil, Kota Larangan, Dataran Tiananmen,

8
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:50,120
Wangfujing, Taman Yuanmingyuan, Istana Musim Panas,

9
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,800
dan Tembok Besar Badaling, semua saya dah jemu pergi.

10
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,440
Orang Beijing sendiri pun tak suka pergi tempat-tempat ini.

11
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,320
Awak pergi mana?

12
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:54,920
Pergi mana?

13
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,960
Cakaplah, awak pergi mana?

14
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:59,840
Tempat-tempat di Beijing itu, Kota Larangan,

15
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,290
Dataran Tiananmen,

16
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,320
Wangfujing,

17
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,770
Istana Musim Panas,

18
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,490
dan Tembok Besar Badaling.

19
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:07,320
Apa yang seronok sangat pergi sana?

20
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,880
Awak tak pergi, kan?

21
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:09,960
Cakap besar sahaja.

22
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,480
Bukan ke orang lain tak pergi, buat apa saya pergi?

23
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,140
Habis itu awak pergi buat apa?

24
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,760
Saya pergi ke sekolah itu dahulu.

25
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,800
Sekolah mereka besar betul.

26
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,760
Jauh lebih baik daripada tempat kita.

27
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:18,760
Kemudian di sana,

28
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,160
saya berkenalan dengan seorang legenda.

29
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,520
Siapa? Legenda?

30
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,600
Di sekolah mereka ada seorang...

31
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,240
pengawal keselamatan.

32
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,520
Pengawal keselamatan? Apa yang hebatnya?

33
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,120
Kenapa pandang rendah pada pengawal keselamatan?

34
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,760
Abang pengawal itu sangat cekap buat kerja.

35
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,640
Hebat betul dia. Itu sahaja.

36
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,280
Ada lagi?

37
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:33,800
Ada.

38
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,400
Kemudian kami pergi ke sebuah lorong misteri.

39
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,560
Orang kata dalam lorong itu ada seorang nenek tua.

40
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:42,280
Sesiapa yang ternampak akan terpikat.

41
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:43,640
Saya dah nampak.

42
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:44,800
Mak cik Hakim.

43
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,560
Awak cakap terang-terang, awak tak pergi mana-mana pun.

44
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,560
Apa yang awak seronokkan sangat di sini?

45
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,640
Apa maksud awak tak pergi mana-mana?

46
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:50,920
Saya dah pergi banyak tempat tau.

47
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,680
Awak ni, macam mana dengan peperiksaan Xiaodan?

48
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,680
Peperiksaan apa?

49
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,400
Awak ni,

50
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:57,000
materialistik. Prosesnya tak penting ke?

51
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,960
Prosesnya lebih indah, awak tahu tak?

52
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,890
Habislah. Kalau dah cakap macam tu, mesti tak lulus.

53
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,680
Apa yang awak merepek ni?

54
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:04,740
Tengoklah.

55
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,600
Dan.

56
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,000
Xiao... Xiaodan.

57
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:07,800
Ini...

58
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,760
Awak tengoklah.

59
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,480
Macam mana?

60
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,580
Kan saya dah cakap.

61
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,380
Kan saya dah cakap.

62
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:16,000
Tak lulus, hanya menikmati prosesnya.

63
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,800
Apa dah jadi dengan kelas kalian ni?

64
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,920
Saya jalan dari sana tadi,

65
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:21,920
kelas kalian saja yang bising.

66
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:24,040
Kelas apa sekarang ni? Mana cikgu?

67
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,520
Pengarah Hou, Cikgu Gu sakit.

68
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,320
Kelas kami belajar sendiri waktu ini.

69
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:28,760
Betul.

70
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:29,560
Belajar sendiri.

71
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:32,160
Kalian faham tak apa itu kelas belajar sendiri?

72
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,160
Ketua kelas, kawal disiplin sikit.

73
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:34,800
Sudahlah, sudahlah.

74
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,880
Semua balik ke tempat duduk. Balik ke tempat duduk.

75
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,540
Baliklah, kelas dah nak mula.

76
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:40,640
Xiaoman, awak kata Cikgu Tong sakit.

77
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,970
Cikgu Dai pun tak sihat.

78
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,960
Sekolah kita ada wabak selesema ke?

79
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,280
Apa selesemanya?

80
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,520
Awak tak tahu lagi ke?

81
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,520
Hampir semua cikgu kelas kita tumbang

82
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,850
disebabkan jeli diraja keluarga Xia Lei.

83
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,120
Apa yang awak buat ni?

84
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,120
Awak nak tunjuk perasaan pada siapa?

85
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:04,720
Kenapa? Bukan ke sebab jeli diraja tak guna ni.

86
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:06,320
Semua guru saya jatuh sakit kerananya.

87
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:07,560
Sekarang satu tingkatan salahkan saya.

88
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,960
Kata keluarga kita jual jeli diraja tak guna ni.

89
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,160
Kenapa cakap dengan mak macam tu?

90
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,800
Mak awak dah penat bekerja seharian.

91
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,160
Balik rumah malam-malam pun kena jual jeli diraja lagi.

92
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,760
Untuk apa semua ni? Bukankah untuk persekolahan awak nanti?

93
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,000
Untuk cari duit lebih untuk keluarga kita?

94
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,000
Awak pula yang nak marah-marah.

95
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:21,760
Nak cari duit lebih, jual jeli diraja tak guna ni?

96
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:22,840
Produk tak berkualiti.

97
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:24,360
Awak... berani awak melawan cakap saya ya?

98
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,640
Saya... mana saya tahu ia akan jadi begini?

99
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:26,560
Kalau saya tahu ia tak berkualiti,

100
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,480
saya tak akan beli. Haih.

101
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:30,000
Mak awak pun kena tipu juga.

102
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,400
Sudah, jangan menangis.

103
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:34,000
Budak ni, kami pun mangsa juga.

104
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,260
Kamu pula yang bising.

105
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,640
Lagipun, tak banyak kotak yang terjual.

106
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:39,240
Beberapa kotak yang terjual itu pun kami dah beli balik.

107
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,240
Kamu tahu tak?

108
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:40,800
Ini...

109
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,520
Kenapa?

110
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,000
Tak ada apa-apa. Saya cuma tanya.

111
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,060
Dah faham ke belum?

112
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,159
Pergi buat kerja sekolah kalau dah faham.

113
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,520
Saya panggil awak makan.

114
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,720
Mak, janganlah marah.

115
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,640
Tak ada apa-apa.

116
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:57,240
Awak tak perlu masuk campur.

117
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,840
Pergi, pergi, pergi.

118
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:04,380
Budak ni, berani dia tinggikan suara pada mak awak.

119
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,770
Macam mana, sayang?

120
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,820
Tindakan saya tadi nampak tak

121
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,160
macam ketua keluarga?

122
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,640
Kenapa awak garang sangat dengan anak?

123
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,920
Kenapa awak garang sangat?

124
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,520
Dia tinggikan suara pada awaklah.

125
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,360
Baiklah, baiklah.

126
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:21,160
Kalau macam tu, saya pergi minta maaf pada dialah.

127
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,520
Tak perlulah.

128
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,120
Tak perlu.

129
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,050
Lain kali lebih berhati-hati, ya.

130
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:26,440
Janganlah minum.

131
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,120
Membazir saja.

132
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,360
Macam mana kalau betul-betul cirit-birit?

133
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,020
Itu sama macam bunuh dirilah.

134
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,170
Memang membazir sikit.

135
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,159
Kalau nak cirit-birit, biarlah kita berdua sekali.

136
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,920
Sudahlah.

137
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,840
Anggap saja perkara ini sudah selesai.

138
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,680
Apalah nasib.

139
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,560
Rajinnya.

140
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,810
Kenapa awak datang?

141
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,520
Tak ada apa-apa. Ayah dan ibu awak dah tidur ke?

142
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,440
Waktu macam ni, mesti dah tidur.

143
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,380
Hari ni selesa sangat.

144
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,320
Nak bawa awak jalan-jalan.

145
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,580
Biar otak segar sikit.

146
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:09,680
Boleh je.

147
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,360
Jom.

148
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,840
Awak ni, kenapa tak tidur malam-malam?

149
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,280
Tak nak tidur.

150
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:24,520
Siang hari, kilang ni penuh orang,

151
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,240
bising sangat.

152
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,290
Itu Kilang Donghua milik semua orang.

153
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:33,120
Bila malam, semua orang dah balik kerja,

154
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,890
kilang ni dah tak ada orang.

155
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,320
Itu Kilang Donghua saya.

156
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,080
Kat sini saya yang berkuasa.

157
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,440
Betapa bebasnya!

158
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,880
Saya cemburu.

159
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:49,120
Saya selalu jalan-jalan atas paip tu waktu malam.

160
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,650
Kilang kita ni banyak paip,

161
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,740
bersambung ke mana-mana,

162
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,440
senang nak pergi mana-mana.

163
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,720
Kalau macam tu, awak kena hati-hati.

164
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,050
Tangga tu dah berkarat.

165
00:06:58,080 --> 00:07:00,080
Jangan sampai terpijak kosong dan jatuh pula.

166
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:02,320
Macam mana awak tahu tangga tu berkarat?

167
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,680
Kilang kita ni dah berapa tahun

168
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,610
tak diselenggara atau diperiksa?

169
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,440
Memang orang bijaklah.

170
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,760
Awak ni, apa nak panggil ya?

171
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,800
Orang bijak tak perlu keluar rumah,

172
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,840
dah tahu hal dunia.

173
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,200
Saya pula lain.

174
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,290
Orang macam saya ni,

175
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,280
orang macam saya ni,

176
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,290
apa-apa hal pun kena tunggu

177
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,360
sampai dah lewat sangat,

178
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:39,480
dah depan mata baru nak sedar.

179
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,810
Kenapa dengan awak?

180
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,920
Tak ada apa-apa.

181
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:53,040
Saya cuma merayau-rayau pada waktu malam.

182
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:56,810
Jalan-jalan tanpa tujuan. Tapi kadang-kadang,

183
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,000
semasa awak berjalan,

184
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,640
awak mungkin akan sampai ke rumah Xiaodan.

185
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:03,440
Bila saya sedar saya dah sampai,

186
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:07,090
saya akan temankannya sekejap di atas paip pemanas.

187
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,360
Tapi paip itu terlalu dekat.

188
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:15,290
Saya boleh dengar Ketua Jurutera Yan bercakap di rumah.

189
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,200
Lepas itu?

190
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:17,960
Lepas itu...

191
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:20,520
Lepas itu?

192
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,360
Ketua Jurutera Yan dah dapat arahan pemindahan.

193
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,890
Dia akan balik ke Shanghai.

194
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:34,179
Xiaodan mungkin akan berpindah selepas peperiksaan masuk universiti.

195
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:39,980
Jadi mereka balik ke Shanghai kali ini bukan sekadar melawat saudara-mara.

196
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:55,040
Xiaodan dah balik ke Shanghai.

197
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,960
Awak pula,

198
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:00,080
kena keluar untuk sambung belajar.

199
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,540
Tinggallah saya seorang.

200
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,000
Awak,

201
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,680
janganlah pesimis sangat.

202
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:13,280
Bukan ke masih ada Dongdong?

203
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,360
Janganlah pesimis.

204
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,720
Siapa kata hanya dengan masuk universiti,

205
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,200
baru boleh tinggalkan Kilang Donghua?

206
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,530
Nanti awak pun boleh kerja di tempat lain.

207
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:25,880
Awak sambung belajar.

208
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,450
Dah fikir nak mohon di mana?

209
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,400
Jauh ke tak?

210
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,720
Saya pun tak tahu.

211
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,040
Saya tak tahu landasan kereta api ini,

212
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,370
boleh bawa saya ke mana.

213
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:45,220
Awak tak pernah terfikir nak keluar tengok dunia luar?

214
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:47,760
Saya tak pernah fikir pun.

215
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,560
Saya rasa kilang kita ini dah cukup bagus.

216
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,560
Kan? Selesa sangat.

217
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,560
Lagipun, awak fikirlah.

218
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:58,250
Kereta api ini, tak kira laju atau jauh mana ia pergi,

219
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:01,960
ia bergerak ikut landasan ini.

220
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:05,480
Lambat-laun ia pasti akan balik ikut jalan yang sama.

221
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,080
Betul tak?

222
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:10,480
Kenapa pula kalau kalian keluar sambung belajar,

223
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:13,050
tak akan balik lagi?

224
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,980
Katakanlah dah tamat pengajian.

225
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,080
Kalau tak kerja di kilang,

226
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,120
saya pun tak tahu nak balik buat apa.

227
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,520
Ayah awak, kan?

228
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:31,720
Pak Cik Ding.

229
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,720
Juga semua pak cik awak yang lain.

230
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,880
Mereka semua bekerja di kilang seumur hidup.

231
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:39,140
Baguslah macam tu, kan? Apa masalahnya?

232
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:43,240
Semua orang kenal satu sama lain, kan?

233
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,640
Kalau ada sesiapa yang ada masalah,

234
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,720
panggil saja, semua orang akan datang.

235
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,520
Semua akan datang menolong.

236
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,400
Bagusnya macam ni.

237
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:54,130
Mana nak cari suasana macam ni?

238
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,800
Mak saya kata,

239
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:03,820
sesetengah orang hanya berteduh di stesen bas.

240
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:08,620
