macam mana nanti?

731
00:41:55,720 --> 00:41:56,880
Saya tak peduli semua ini.

732
00:41:56,880 --> 00:41:57,810
Apa masalahnya?

733
00:41:57,880 --> 00:41:59,160
Xiaoman dah ditahan.

734
00:41:59,280 --> 00:42:00,200
Awak perempuan.

735
00:42:00,200 --> 00:42:00,860
Dia lelaki.

736
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:01,520
Tak sama.

737
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,650
Balik, cepat masuk.

738
00:42:02,680 --> 00:42:03,680
Sudah, masuklah.

739
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:12,650
Saya akan pergi ke balai polis.

740
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:16,780
Awak jangan risau.

741
00:42:17,520 --> 00:42:19,320
Saya akan sampaikan semua fakta yang awak beritahu ini

742
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:21,560
kepada pihak polis dengan terperinci.

743
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:25,450
Kita akan cuba sedaya upaya agar Xiaoman tidak dianiaya, okey?

744
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:28,120
Awak jaga dia di rumah.

745
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:29,650
Jangan pergi ke mana-mana.

746
00:42:30,200 --> 00:42:31,000
Dengar cakap.

747
00:42:50,360 --> 00:42:53,320
Nannan, ibu tahu awak risau,

748
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:55,640
tapi kalau awak pergi pun tiada gunanya.

749
00:42:55,640 --> 00:42:57,760
Betul tak? Awak kan masih budak.

750
00:42:58,720 --> 00:42:59,780
Pergi pun tak guna.

751
00:42:59,880 --> 00:43:00,440
Okey?

752
00:43:00,520 --> 00:43:01,960
Mari, mari, masuklah.

753
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:04,160
Baiklah, dah masuk ya, Nannan.

